; Simple Survex centerline used by the external-centerline scanner
; tests and the [Attach][Trip]/[Attach][Mixed] driver-emission tests.
; Self-fixing (*fix A1 at origin) so the attached scope cavern emits
; positions for even when the parent driver has no shared station to
; connect against.
*begin Simple
*fix A1 0 0 0
*data normal from to tape compass clino
A1 A2 10.0 0 0
A2 A3 8.5 90 0
*end Simple
